{"tid":1675661,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[黃色經濟圈] 戰略上其實我地應該更加接納藍轉黃商戶","createTime":"2019-10-26T04:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T08:03:09.000Z","uid":1915,"like":52,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"abfb9d42fcc5bce2180a1eded7e92991d723da86","tid":1675661,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n如果支共殺到黎 <br />\n你投降都係要死的話<br />\n咁你一定係會係死前盡力殺敵然後先死<br />\n<br />\n依家一樣 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果我地見到藍轉黃既商店都係一面倒屌撚柒佢唔幫襯<br />\n咁就唔會收歸到其他藍店</span><br />\n當然有一個<span style=\"color: red;\">轉色條件</span><br />\n例如<span style=\"color: red;\">必需最少係page及門市公開指明反警或撐普選</span>等<br />\n條件要比正常黃嚴格，以避免講句香港人加油模稜兩可食兩家茶禮"},{"pid":"09364c25084a8e85be04e839e5946638206176e1","tid":1675661,"uid":224095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"應該要接受招降成功個啲<br />\n<br />\n但騎牆中立就算"},{"pid":"61de3492c3dc5734a6ecfcf3ace91c89837fac29","tid":1675661,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">聽日3點 梳士巴利花園集合<br />\n夠人就出發<br />\n❌不需要不反對通知書❌</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOz1dRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOz1dRB.jpg&h=0ccb728d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c51583ff92c9299c76ec634ff560777962ff229a","tid":1675661,"uid":1915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"09364c25084a8e85be04e839e5946638206176e1","tid":1675661,"uid":224095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"應該要接受招降成功個啲<br />\n<br />\n但騎牆中立就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"所以要設立嚴格轉色條件<br />\n等佢冇得騎牆<br />\n一轉黃就轉唔番藍"},{"pid":"7382e4657f134e28733b7642d54a4d64dba02220","tid":1675661,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:58:58.000Z","msg"